t use a likelihood of the biased tracer at\nthe field level, or for initial condition and BAO reconstruction that requires\na precise estimate of the large-scale potential from the biased tracer density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 19:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 13:21:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
