variety of cloudy rocky planets, and increase our confidence in future\nsimulations of temperature profile and net energy balance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2018 00:46:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-28"}
