lutions\nto the system are globally bounded and decay to a spatially homogeneous\nequilibrium exponentially as time goes to infinity. In addition, we will also\nshow that, for any $\\alpha\\geq 0$, a similar result is valid when the initial\ndata satisfy a certain smallness condition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2018 10:01:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
